| dead-url=no
}}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web |language =en |url =http://www2.kenyon.edu/Depts/Religion/Fac/Adler/Reln275/Jap-Kor-art.htm |title =Japanese Art and Its Korean Secret |date =2003-04-06 |publisher =kenyon.edu |author =HOLLAND COTTER |accessdate =2008-10-09 |archive-date =2011-07-09 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110709082157/http://www2.kenyon.edu/Depts/Religion/Fac/Adler/Reln275/Jap-Kor-art.htm |dead-url =yes }}</ref>
<ref name="sandai">{{cite web| language=en| publisher=増田建築研究所ホームページ| title=JAPANESE ARCHITECTURE IN KYOTO| url=http://orion.fken.ise.osaka-sandai.ac.jp/orion/eng/hstj/ukyo/koryuji.html| author=| date=| accessdate=| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090321102435/http://orion.fken.ise.osaka-sandai.ac.jp/orion/eng/hstj/ukyo/koryuji.html| archivedate=2009-03-21}}</ref>
三國時期的[[佛教|佛教]]促使大量佛寺的興建，譬如百濟的[[彌勒寺|彌勒寺]]（Mireuksa）與新羅的[[皇龍寺|皇龍寺]]（Hwangnyongsa）。百濟的建築師都以工藝及興建皇龍寺的九層寶塔而聞名。<ref name="banister">{{cite book
|language=en
|title=Sir Banister Fletcher's a History of Architecture: A History of Architecture
|author=Banister Fletcher, Dan Cruickshank
|publisher=Architectural Press
|year=1996
|ISBN=9780750622677
|url=http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0750622679&id=Gt1jTpXAThwC&pg=PA716&lpg=PA716&vq=horyuji&dq=horyuji&sig=hiMUDjxVEe938FZSZioeaLY_eGg
|access-date=2008-10-09
|archive-date=2014-05-02
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502003544/http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0750622679&id=Gt1jTpXAThwC&pg=PA716&lpg=PA716&vq=horyuji&dq=horyuji&sig=hiMUDjxVEe938FZSZioeaLY_eGg
|dead-url=no
}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language=en| url=http://www.orientalarchitecture.com/nara/horyujiindex.htm| title=Horyuji Temple  (7th-8th centuries onward)| publisher=orientalarchitecture.com| accessdate=2008-10-09| archive-date=2020-12-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205142540/https://www.orientalarchitecture.com/nara/horyujiindex.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web 
 |language=en 
 |url=http://www.indiana.edu/~easc/resources/korea_slides/architecture/3-2.htm 
